<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0015/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "rencana tata ruang pulau/kepulauanj," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0015/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0015/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/point/b/text> .
