<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam rangka menyelenggarakan tugas sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 13 dan Pasal 14, Kepolisian Negara Republik Indonesia secara umum berwenang:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "menerima laporan dan/atau pengaduan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "membantu menyelesaikan perselisihan warga masyarakat yang dapat mengganggu ketertiban umum," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString ". mencegah dan menanggulangi tumbuhnya penyakit masyarakat," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "mengawasi aliran yang dapat menimbulkan perpecahan atau mengancam persatuan dan kesatuan bangsa," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "mengeluarkan peraturan kepolisian dalam lingkup kewenangan administratif kepolisian," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "melaksanakan pemeriksaan khusus sebagai bagian dari tindakan kepolisian dalam rangka pencegahan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "melakukan tindakan pertama di tempat kejadian," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/h> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/h> legal:pointHasKey "h" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0075/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/h/text> legal:textHasTextString "mengambil sidik jari dan identitas lainnya serta memotret seseorang," .
