<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0129/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tanah yang dikelola badan bank tanah diberikan hak pengelolaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0129/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0129/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/text> .
