<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam keadaan tertentu, Pemerintah Pusat dapat membatalkan dan/atau mencabut hak pengelolaan sebagian atau seluruhnya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tata cara pembatalan hak pengelolaan dilaksanakan sesuai dengan ketentuan peraturan-perundang- undangan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0139/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0008/bagian/0004/paragraf/0002/pasals> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0140> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0140> legal:pasalHasKey 140 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0140> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0140/version/0000000000> .
