<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144> legal:pasalHasKey 144 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000> .
