<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Hak milik atas satuan rumah susun dapat diberikan kepada:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "warga negara Indonesia," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "badan hukum Indonesia:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "warga negara asing yang mempunyai izin sesuai ketentuan peraturan perundang-undangan," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "badan hukum asing yang mempunyai perwakilan di Indonesia: atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "perwakilan negara asing dan lembaga internasional yang berada atau mempunyai perwakilan di Indonesia." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> legal:textHasTextString "Hak milik atas satuan rumah susun dapat beralih atau dialihkan dan dijaminkan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0144/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> legal:textHasTextString "Hak milik atas satuan rumah susun dapat dijaminkan dengan dibebani hak tanggungan sesuai dengan ketentuan peraturan perundang-undangan." .
