<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Rumah susun dapat dibangun di atas Tanah:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "hak guna bangunan atau hak pakai di atas tanah negara, atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "hak guna bangunan atau hak pakai di atas tanah hak pengelolaan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemberian hak guna bangunan bagi rumah susun sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) huruf a dapat diberikan sekaligus dengan perpanjangan haknya setelah mendapat sertifikat laik fungsi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pemberian hak guna bangunan bagi rumah susun sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) huruf b dapat diberikan perpanjangan dan pembaharuan hak apabila sudah mendapat sertifikat laik fungsi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0145/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0008/bagian/0004/paragraf> legal:paragrafSetHasParagraf <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0008/bagian/0004/paragraf/0004> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0008/bagian/0004/paragraf/0004> legal:paragrafHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0008/bagian/0004/paragraf/0004> legal:paragrafHasTitle "Paragraf 4 Pemberian Hak atas Tanah/Hak Pengelolaan pada Ruang atas Tanah dan Ruang Bawah Tanah" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0008/bagian/0004/paragraf/0004> legal:paragrafHasPasalSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0008/bagian/0004/paragraf/0004/pasals> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0008/bagian/0004/paragraf/0004/pasals> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0146> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0146> legal:pasalHasKey 146 .
