<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> legal:textHasTextString "Aset Lembaga dapat dijaminkan dalam rangka penarikan pinjaman." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pihak manapun dilarang melakukan penyitaan aset Lembaga, kecuali atas aset yang telah dijaminkan dalam rangka pinjaman." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0004> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0004> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0004/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengelolaan aset Lembaga sepenuhnya dilakukan oleh organ Lembaga berdasarkan prinsip tata kelola yang baik, akuntabel, dan transparan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0004> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0160/version/0000000000/ayat/0004/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0010/bagian/0001/paragraf/0001/pasals> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0161> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0161> legal:pasalHasKey 161 .
