<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/text> legal:textHasTextString "Organ dan pegawai Lembaga bukan merupakan penyelengara negara, kecuali yang berasal dari pejabat negara yang bersifat ex-officio." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga menetapkan sistem kepegawaian, sistem penggajian, penghargaan, program pensiun dan tunjangan hari tua, serta penghasilan lainnya bagi pegawai Lembaga." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> legal:textHasTextString "Lembaga tidak dapat dipailitkan, kecuali dapat dibuktikan dalam kondisi insolven." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0162/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0010/bagian/0001/paragraf/0001/pasals> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163> legal:pasalHasKey 163 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000> .
