<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000> legal:pasalVersionHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Menteri Keuangan, pejabat Kementerian Keuangan, dan organ dan pegawai Lembaga, tidak dapat dimintai pertanggungjawaban hukum atas kerugian investasi jika dapat membuktikan:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "kerugian tersebut bukan karena kesalahan atau kelalaiannya," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "telah melakukan pengurusan dengan iktikad baik dan kehati-hatian sesuai dengan maksud dan tujuan investasi dan tata kelola," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "tidak memiliki benturan kepentingan, baik langsung maupun tidak langsung atas tindakan pengelolaan investasi, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0163/version/0000000000/point/d> .
