<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0165/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Organ Lembaga Pengelola Investasi terdiri atas:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0165/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0165/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/point/description> .
