<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Dewan Pengawas sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 165 ayat (3) huruf a terdiri atas:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/description> .
