<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "Menteri yang menyelenggarakan urusan pemerintahan di bidang badan usaha milik negara sebagai anggota, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0166/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/point/c> .
