<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dewan Direktur sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 165 ayat (3) huruf b berjumlah 5 (lima) orang dari unsur profesional." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0001> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0001/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anggota Dewan Direktur sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) diangkat dan diberhentikan oleh Dewan Pengawas." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0002> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0002/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> legal:textHasTextString "Sesama anggota Dewan Direktur dilarang saling memiliki hubungan keluarga sampai derajat kedua atau besan dengan sesama anggota Dewan Direktur dan/atau dengan anggota Dewan Pengawas." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0003> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0003/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0004> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0004> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0004/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anggota Dewan Direktur diangkat untuk masa jabatan 5 (lima) tahun dan hanya dapat diangkat kembali untuk 1 (satu) kali masa jabatan berikutnya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0004> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0004/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam rangka pengangkatan anggota Dewan Direktur untuk pertama kali, Dewan Pengawas menetapkan masa jabatan 5 (lima) anggota Dewan Direktur sebagai berikut:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "2 (dua) anggota diangkat untuk masa jabatan 5 (lima) tahun," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "2 (dua) anggota diangkat untuk masa jabatan 4 (empat) tahun, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "1 (satu) anggota diangkat untuk masa jabatan 3 (tiga) tahun." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0005/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0006> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0006> legal:ayatHasKey 6 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0006/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dewan Direktur sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) bertugas untuk menyelenggarakan pengurusan operasional Lembaga Pengelola Investasi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0006> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0006/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007> legal:ayatHasKey 7 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam menjalankan tugas sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (6), Dewan Direktur berwenang:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "merumuskan dan menetapkan kebijakan lembaga," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "melaksanakan kebijakan dan pengurusan operasional lembaga," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "menyusun dan mengusulkan remunerasi Dewan Pengawas dan Dewan Direktur kepada Dewan Pengawas," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "menyusun dan mengusulkan rencana kerja dan anggaran tahunan beserta indikator kinerja utama (key performance indicator) kepada Dewan Pengawas," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "menyusun struktur organisasi lembaga dan menyelenggarakan manajemen kepegawaian termasuk pengangkatan, pemberhentian, sistem penggajian, remunerasi penghargaan, program pensiun dan tunjangan hari tua, serta penghasilan lainnya bagi pegawai Lembaga Pengelola Investasi, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "mewakili Lembaga Pengelola Investasi di dalam dan di luar pengadilan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0007/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0008> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0008> legal:ayatHasKey 8 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0008/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dewan Direktur dapat mendelegasikan tugas dan/atau wewenang pelaksanaan operasional Lembaga Pengelola Investasi kepada pegawai Lembaga Pengelola Investasi dan/atau pihak lain yang khusus ditunjuk untuk itu." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0008> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0008/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0009> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0009> legal:ayatHasKey 9 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0009/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pembidangan setiap anggota Dewan Direktur ditetapkan oleh Dewan Direktur." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0009> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0167/version/0000000000/ayat/0009/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/bab/0010/bagian/0001/paragraf/0002/pasals> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168> legal:pasalHasKey 168 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168/version/0000000000> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168/version/0000000000> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168/version/0000000000> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168/version/0000000000> legal:pasalVersionHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168/version/0000000000/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168/version/0000000000/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk dapat diangkat sebagai anggota Dewan Pengawas dari unsur profesional dan anggota Dewan Direktur, calon anggota Dewan Pengawas dari unsur profesional dan calon anggota Dewan Direktur harus memenuhi persyaratan:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168/version/0000000000/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0168/version/0000000000/point/description> .
