<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0185/version/0000000000/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "Peraturan pelaksanaan dari Undang-Undang ini wajib ditetapkan paling lama 3 (tiga) bulan, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0185/version/0000000000/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0185/version/0000000000/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0185/version/0000000000/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/0185/version/0000000000/point/b> .
